Package: vectra
Title: Columnar Query Engine for Larger-Than-RAM Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gilles", "Colling", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "gilles.colling@boku.ac.at")
Description: A minimal columnar query engine with lazy execution on datasets
    larger than RAM. Provides dplyr-like verbs (filter, select, mutate,
    group_by, summarise) backed by a pure C11 pull-based execution engine
    and a custom on-disk format (.vtr).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    tidyselect,
    rlang
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Suggests:
    bit64,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
